data.description: Welcome to this Fully Updated Ranch with a Fully Unfinished Basement!  1st Floor Living with Lot of Open Basement Space to Finish or use for storage. Including a 2nd set of Laundry Connections, so you have the option of main floor laundry currently or a 2nd laundry Room in the Basement or relocate existing first floor connections to utilize that space for something else. Corner Lot, with a nice size Lot size which is Amazing for Entertaining.  Everything in the Dining Room Stays as a Set.  All Brand New Appliances Stay, Home has Security System lines available but buyer would need to get their own equipment out company to install new system. Property previously Fully Water proofed in 2022, All New Windows in 2017. A Brand New Additional Full Bathroom with Walk-in Shower Added along with a Bluetooth Speaker/Exhaust Fan Installed to the Master Bedroom, making this a 3 Bed 3 bath Home!  Property comes with a Fully Functioning Above ground pool that is emptied and covered, New buyer would just need to have it cleaned and opened up for the season. New Luxury Vinyl Flooring Installed through the home, New Dishwasher installed, New Linoleum Flooring in the main floor laundry room, among many more updates throughout the Home!
